WEBVTT

00:00:00.160 --> 00:00:03.709
Good morning, family. I tried to

00:00:03.719 --> 00:00:07.070
get a video out yesterday, and we had

00:00:07.080 --> 00:00:09.709
it all recorded, but I didn't realize the

00:00:09.719 --> 00:00:12.190
neighbor was working in the yard.

00:00:12.200 --> 00:00:14.190
I could hear him, but I didn't

00:00:14.200 --> 00:00:15.869
realize how much it picked up in the

00:00:15.879 --> 00:00:18.150
background and messed up the video. It

00:00:18.150 --> 00:00:18.160
sounded

00:00:18.160 --> 00:00:20.390
like he was using his

00:00:20.400 --> 00:00:22.189
blower to blow the leaves off from the

00:00:22.199 --> 00:00:26.029
fall. I just told him,

00:00:26.039 --> 00:00:27.910
'Let's just do it

00:00:27.910 --> 00:00:27.920
over,'as

00:00:27.920 --> 00:00:29.990
frustrating as it is after you've taken

00:00:29.990 --> 00:00:30.000
an

00:00:30.000 --> 00:00:32.109
hour of your time to do that.

00:00:32.119 --> 00:00:34.590
But it

00:00:34.600 --> 00:00:36.790
wasn't meant to be. What was cool was

00:00:36.800 --> 00:00:38.670
when Diana and I were

00:00:38.680 --> 00:00:41.750
praying outside in the yard,

00:00:41.760 --> 00:00:44.590
there were two bald eagles flying over.

00:00:44.600 --> 00:00:46.750
When we were praying for America and for

00:00:46.760 --> 00:00:48.950
the United States, they were flying over

00:00:48.960 --> 00:00:50.830
and circling. It

00:00:50.830 --> 00:00:50.840
was

00:00:50.840 --> 00:00:53.229
really touching

00:00:53.239 --> 00:00:54.990
because it was just at that moment when

00:00:55.000 --> 00:00:57.229
we started praying for President

00:00:57.239 --> 00:01:00.270
Trump that those eagles came down,

00:01:00.280 --> 00:01:01.910
landed in the trees, and

00:01:01.910 --> 00:01:01.920
circled

00:01:01.920 --> 00:01:03.790
us. It

00:01:03.800 --> 00:01:07.710
was really a cool moment.

00:01:12.200 --> 00:01:16.789
Billy Burke is coming to Tulsa,

00:01:16.799 --> 00:01:20.670
Oklahoma, December 8th and 9th.

00:01:20.680 --> 00:01:23.510
He's coming to Millennial Church.

00:01:23.520 --> 00:01:26.069
A lot of people are always

00:01:26.079 --> 00:01:28.789
asking me, 'Brandon, can you let us

00:01:28.799 --> 00:01:30.590
know whenever you know of a meeting where you believe the glory is

00:01:30.590 --> 00:01:30.600
going to show up?'This is one

00:01:30.600 --> 00:01:32.590
that I believe has the

00:01:32.590 --> 00:01:32.600
opportunity. I believe

00:01:32.600 --> 00:01:36.429
the glory of God's going to show up

00:01:40.280 --> 00:01:42.670
here on the

00:01:42.680 --> 00:01:45.429
8th and 9th at Millennial

00:01:45.439 --> 00:01:47.190
Church in Tulsa, Oklahoma. I would

00:01:47.200 --> 00:01:49.950
encourage anyone, if he's in your area, to

00:01:49.950 --> 00:01:49.960
pull up

00:01:49.960 --> 00:01:53.190
his itinerary.

00:01:53.200 --> 00:01:55.310
My son puts up new

00:01:55.320 --> 00:01:57.350
meetings all the time.

00:01:57.360 --> 00:01:59.389
Go and support Billy Burke. If you

00:01:59.389 --> 00:01:59.399
get to

00:01:59.399 --> 00:02:01.429
go

00:02:01.439 --> 00:02:03.029
to the front and he prays for you and

00:02:03.029 --> 00:02:03.039
asks

00:02:03.039 --> 00:02:04.670
where you're from, just tell him

00:02:04.680 --> 00:02:07.630
Brandon sent you from YouTube. He'll

00:02:07.640 --> 00:02:09.589
probably get a kick out of that because

00:02:09.599 --> 00:02:12.470
I've sent a lot of people to him

00:02:12.480 --> 00:02:14.949
through this channel. I

00:02:14.949 --> 00:02:14.959
believe in

00:02:14.959 --> 00:02:17.830
him

00:02:20.229 --> 00:02:20.239
and

00:02:23.080 --> 00:02:24.790
the outpouring that

00:02:24.790 --> 00:02:24.800
is coming—the

00:02:24.800 --> 00:02:27.070
creative miracles and

00:02:27.080 --> 00:02:29.309
manifestations of

00:02:29.319 --> 00:02:31.430
power. This is a time like we've

00:02:31.440 --> 00:02:33.309
never seen before. I believe we're

00:02:33.319 --> 00:02:35.830
going to start to see a move of God in

00:02:35.840 --> 00:02:38.190
America and around the world. Billy

00:02:38.200 --> 00:02:40.390
Burke is a vessel the

00:02:40.400 --> 00:02:43.509
Lord is using to bring forth

00:02:43.519 --> 00:02:45.070
healings.

00:02:45.080 --> 00:02:47.390
I'm excited for

00:02:47.400 --> 00:02:49.110
his ministry because when I went

00:02:49.120 --> 00:02:51.190
last time to

00:02:51.190 --> 00:02:51.200
Eufaula,

00:02:51.200 --> 00:02:53.030
Oklahoma,

00:02:53.040 --> 00:02:55.430
the presence of the Lord was

00:02:55.430 --> 00:02:55.440
radically

00:02:55.440 --> 00:02:58.190
strong. It changed me

00:02:58.200 --> 00:03:01.630
forever. I've been

00:03:04.560 --> 00:03:06.990
a meeting junkie, going around trying to

00:03:07.000 --> 00:03:09.309
find where

00:03:09.319 --> 00:03:11.509
the Spirit of the Lord is moving, but

00:03:11.519 --> 00:03:13.750
it was the strongest there.

00:03:13.760 --> 00:03:16.110
I

00:03:16.120 --> 00:03:17.949
encourage

00:03:21.799 --> 00:03:24.750
you to come to Millennial Church.

00:03:27.440 --> 00:03:28.869
It's not a big

00:03:28.879 --> 00:03:32.470
church, so seating might

00:03:32.480 --> 00:03:35.190
be

00:03:35.200 --> 00:03:36.949
limited.

00:03:36.959 --> 00:03:39.149
He

00:03:39.159 --> 00:03:41.509
goes to Pittsburgh, Canada, Florida, and California a lot.

00:03:49.439 --> 00:03:51.070
If

00:03:51.080 --> 00:03:52.390
you have the

00:03:52.400 --> 00:03:54.589
opportunity,

00:03:54.599 --> 00:03:57.030
be there.

00:03:57.040 --> 00:03:59.429
The second thing is that

00:03:59.439 --> 00:04:03.149
Sister Billye Brim and

00:04:03.159 --> 00:04:07.670
Rick Renner are going to do a

00:04:07.680 --> 00:04:12.710
conference at

00:04:12.720 --> 00:04:14.589
Glorious Church

00:04:14.599 --> 00:04:17.390
Fellowship with Pastor Chip Brim. They're

00:04:17.400 --> 00:04:21.349
going to do a meeting for a week

00:04:21.359 --> 00:04:24.310
talking about end times, the

00:04:24.320 --> 00:04:27.189
Rapture, and

00:04:27.199 --> 00:04:28.550
the

00:04:28.560 --> 00:04:30.950
Thousand-Year Reign,

00:04:30.950 --> 00:04:30.960
backing

00:04:30.960 --> 00:04:34.110
it up with

00:04:34.120 --> 00:04:38.189
scripture.

00:04:40.199 --> 00:04:42.430
Rick Renner is an expert in the

00:04:42.440 --> 00:04:46.830
Greek, and Billye is an expert in prophecy

00:04:46.840 --> 00:04:49.510
and

00:04:49.510 --> 00:04:49.520
end-time

00:04:49.520 --> 00:04:51.749
eschatology.

00:04:54.199 --> 00:04:56.390
They've never done a

00:04:56.400 --> 00:04:57.710
meeting

00:04:57.720 --> 00:05:01.909
together teaching on end-time stuff.

00:05:08.160 --> 00:05:10.390
It's going to be

00:05:10.400 --> 00:05:13.150
in February

00:05:25.560 --> 00:05:28.230
2025.

00:05:33.840 --> 00:05:35.790
We're

00:05:35.800 --> 00:05:37.790
excited to

00:05:37.800 --> 00:05:39.909
hear the

00:05:39.909 --> 00:05:39.919
end-time

00:05:39.919 --> 00:05:43.629
teachings and get our

00:05:43.629 --> 00:05:43.639
tanks

00:05:43.639 --> 00:05:46.150
filled up for the new

00:05:46.160 --> 00:05:47.749
year.

00:05:47.759 --> 00:05:50.230
Start out with Billy Burke,

00:05:50.230 --> 00:05:50.240
Billye

00:05:50.240 --> 00:05:52.870
Brim, and

00:05:52.880 --> 00:05:55.710
Rick

00:06:05.560 --> 00:06:07.390
Renner.

00:06:16.919 --> 00:06:19.110
I'm not sponsoring these; they

00:06:19.120 --> 00:06:21.350
didn't ask me. I

00:06:21.360 --> 00:06:23.589
just felt in my heart

00:06:23.599 --> 00:06:26.029
to

00:06:27.550 --> 00:06:27.560
share

00:06:29.199 --> 00:06:31.749
these two

00:06:31.759 --> 00:06:33.390
meetings.

00:06:33.400 --> 00:06:36.670
I

00:06:36.680 --> 00:06:38.270
want to

00:06:41.360 --> 00:06:43.670
share

00:06:45.160 --> 00:06:46.950
a

00:06:46.960 --> 00:06:49.950
testimony. Remember Diana

00:06:49.960 --> 00:06:53.270
prayed for people to

00:06:57.160 --> 00:07:00.749
conceive?

00:07:00.759 --> 00:07:04.830
In the last week, she's had

00:07:04.840 --> 00:07:08.670
several emails from ladies

00:07:08.680 --> 00:07:11.270
saying they were able to

00:07:17.400 --> 00:07:20.869
get

00:07:20.879 --> 00:07:25.629
pregnant this

00:07:25.639 --> 00:07:29.270
month after believing

00:07:29.270 --> 00:07:29.280
for a

00:07:29.280 --> 00:07:31.350
long time.

00:07:31.350 --> 00:07:31.360
I

00:07:31.360 --> 00:07:34.230
give all

00:07:34.240 --> 00:07:38.469
the glory to God.

00:07:44.469 --> 00:07:44.479
One

00:07:51.919 --> 00:07:53.990
had

00:07:53.990 --> 00:07:54.000
been

00:07:57.869 --> 00:07:57.879
trying

00:07:57.879 --> 00:07:59.990
for

00:08:00.000 --> 00:08:02.869
several years,

00:08:04.240 --> 00:08:05.350
and the doctor said

00:08:05.350 --> 00:08:05.360
it

00:08:05.360 --> 00:08:07.309
wouldn't

00:08:07.309 --> 00:08:07.319
happen,

00:08:07.319 --> 00:08:09.430
but

00:08:09.440 --> 00:08:11.189
the Lord blessed them.

00:08:11.199 --> 00:08:14.029
We're believing

00:08:16.390 --> 00:08:16.400
for

00:08:19.240 --> 00:08:21.430
full-term,

00:08:21.440 --> 00:08:24.670
healthy

00:08:37.670 --> 00:08:37.680
babies.

00:08:54.240 --> 00:08:57.949
Diana

00:08:57.949 --> 00:08:57.959
read

00:08:57.959 --> 00:09:00.630
'Supernatural

00:09:00.640 --> 00:09:02.269
Childbirth,'and

00:09:02.279 --> 00:09:04.949
we

00:09:04.959 --> 00:09:06.590
took communion every day.

00:09:06.600 --> 00:09:09.269
She

00:09:09.269 --> 00:09:09.279
said,

00:09:09.279 --> 00:09:10.790
'Brandon, I'm

00:09:10.800 --> 00:09:13.230
going to have a supernatural childbirth

00:09:13.230 --> 00:09:13.240
and

00:09:13.240 --> 00:09:14.990
experience no pain.'I agreed

00:09:14.990 --> 00:09:15.000
with her. We looked

00:09:15.000 --> 00:09:17.470
at

00:09:21.000 --> 00:09:22.829
the

00:09:26.440 --> 00:09:29.030
scripture

00:09:34.000 --> 00:09:35.269
about

00:09:35.279 --> 00:09:37.870
how

00:09:37.880 --> 00:09:40.310
the

00:09:40.320 --> 00:09:43.350
Hebrew

00:09:43.360 --> 00:09:45.829
women

00:09:55.480 --> 00:09:58.829
had easy births compared to the Egyptians. We

00:09:58.839 --> 00:10:00.790
latched onto that scripture.

00:10:11.079 --> 00:10:13.750
At the

00:10:13.760 --> 00:10:17.710
hospital,

00:10:17.720 --> 00:10:21.069
the

00:10:21.079 --> 00:10:23.350
doctors

00:10:23.360 --> 00:10:25.670
didn't think

00:10:25.680 --> 00:10:27.509
she was in labor because she wasn't

00:10:27.519 --> 00:10:29.870
in agony.

00:10:29.880 --> 00:10:32.790
They thought it

00:10:32.790 --> 00:10:32.800
was

00:10:32.800 --> 00:10:35.910
Braxton Hicks,

00:10:40.920 --> 00:10:43.269
but

00:10:43.279 --> 00:10:46.949
her

00:10:46.959 --> 00:10:49.550
water had broken. Her contractions were high,

00:10:49.550 --> 00:10:49.560
but she felt no pain.

00:10:49.560 --> 00:10:51.829
They

00:10:53.550 --> 00:10:53.560
tried

00:10:58.110 --> 00:10:58.120
to

00:11:02.150 --> 00:11:02.160
pressure

00:11:03.800 --> 00:11:07.350
her

00:11:10.079 --> 00:11:12.949
into

00:11:15.079 --> 00:11:17.350
an

00:11:17.360 --> 00:11:20.030
epidural,

00:11:32.440 --> 00:11:34.590
but

00:11:48.079 --> 00:11:49.710
she

00:12:00.000 --> 00:12:01.190
refused.

00:12:11.600 --> 00:12:14.829
I

00:12:25.120 --> 00:12:26.829
saw

00:12:39.720 --> 00:12:42.110
in the spirit

00:12:42.120 --> 00:12:45.790
realm an angel touching her stomach and her back the

00:12:45.800 --> 00:12:49.269
whole time.

00:13:41.680 --> 00:13:43.430
But then doubt and fear entered the room from the doctors and visitors. When Diana started

00:13:52.150 --> 00:13:52.160
doubting

00:14:01.440 --> 00:14:03.030
because

00:14:22.240 --> 00:14:24.990
of

00:14:40.189 --> 00:14:40.199
the

00:14:54.230 --> 00:14:54.240
environment,

00:15:10.639 --> 00:15:12.629
I saw the

00:15:12.639 --> 00:15:15.150
angel take his hand off and

00:15:15.160 --> 00:15:17.790
disappear.

00:15:21.399 --> 00:15:23.829
Jesus had to tell the unbelievers

00:15:23.829 --> 00:15:23.839
to leave

00:15:23.839 --> 00:15:26.389
the room

00:15:26.399 --> 00:15:28.030
when he raised the

00:15:28.040 --> 00:15:29.749
little girl.

00:16:13.399 --> 00:16:17.350
We didn't do that,

00:16:17.350 --> 00:16:17.360
and

00:16:17.360 --> 00:16:19.350
it

00:16:19.360 --> 00:16:23.069
robbed

00:16:23.069 --> 00:16:23.079
the

00:16:23.079 --> 00:16:25.309
blessing.

00:16:25.319 --> 00:16:27.550
She went from feeling

00:16:27.560 --> 00:16:30.269
nothing to

00:16:30.279 --> 00:16:32.629
excruciating pain

00:16:32.639 --> 00:16:34.670
instantly.

00:16:38.430 --> 00:16:38.440
I

00:16:41.040 --> 00:16:44.069
was

00:16:45.629 --> 00:16:45.639
yelling

00:16:47.360 --> 00:16:49.470
at the

00:16:49.470 --> 00:16:49.480
wall,

00:16:49.480 --> 00:16:51.230
'Where

00:16:51.230 --> 00:16:51.240
did

00:16:51.240 --> 00:16:52.550
the

00:16:52.550 --> 00:16:52.560
angel

00:16:52.560 --> 00:16:55.430
go?'Fear

00:16:55.440 --> 00:16:59.509
tolerated is faith

00:16:59.519 --> 00:17:02.309
contaminated.

00:17:07.480 --> 00:17:08.990
Megan

00:17:13.959 --> 00:17:15.590
was

00:17:17.919 --> 00:17:19.630
delivered

00:17:23.360 --> 00:17:25.230
healthy

00:17:30.440 --> 00:17:33.270
with

00:18:28.149 --> 00:18:28.159
perfect

00:19:20.720 --> 00:19:22.430
Apgar

00:20:11.000 --> 00:20:14.230
scores.

00:28:05.399 --> 00:28:07.389
We're still

00:28:07.399 --> 00:28:12.350
learning.

00:31:09.679 --> 00:31:11.789
We're not

00:31:11.799 --> 00:31:13.549
moved by what we see. We're

00:31:13.559 --> 00:31:16.149
believing

00:31:16.159 --> 00:31:18.190
Megan will fully talk and be

00:31:18.200 --> 00:31:20.669
completely healed from autism.

00:31:24.840 --> 00:31:28.470
God

00:31:45.430 --> 00:31:45.440
wants

00:32:00.480 --> 00:32:02.669
to show up and show off in your

00:32:02.679 --> 00:32:04.870
life, just like He did with the blind

00:32:04.880 --> 00:32:06.470
child, with blind Bartimaeus, and

00:32:06.470 --> 00:32:06.480
the woman

00:32:06.480 --> 00:32:07.830
with the

00:32:07.840 --> 00:32:10.029
issue of blood.

00:32:36.320 --> 00:32:38.070
Do you believe Jesus will

00:32:38.080 --> 00:32:39.549
heal

00:32:39.559 --> 00:32:42.230
you?

00:33:11.960 --> 00:33:14.269
Blind Bartimaeus and

00:33:14.269 --> 00:33:14.279
the woman with

00:33:14.279 --> 00:33:15.070
the issue of

00:33:15.070 --> 00:33:15.080
blood waited

00:33:15.080 --> 00:33:18.070
years.

00:33:18.080 --> 00:33:22.590
She

00:33:47.200 --> 00:33:50.909
touched the hem of His

00:33:50.919 --> 00:33:54.750
garment

00:33:54.750 --> 00:33:54.760
and

00:33:54.760 --> 00:33:58.549
was

00:33:58.559 --> 00:34:01.750
made whole.

00:34:17.280 --> 00:34:20.030
You've got to

00:34:20.040 --> 00:34:22.230
say it and

00:34:22.240 --> 00:34:24.510
receive it.

00:34:35.520 --> 00:34:37.669
Jesus already did

00:34:37.669 --> 00:34:37.679
the

00:34:37.679 --> 00:34:39.990
work.

00:34:40.000 --> 00:34:44.069
He

00:34:45.560 --> 00:34:49.349
took

00:34:51.919 --> 00:34:54.669
all sickness,

00:34:54.679 --> 00:34:57.790
disease, poverty,

00:35:00.280 --> 00:35:05.190
and

00:35:07.800 --> 00:35:10.550
addictions.

00:35:13.320 --> 00:35:15.829
Christ redeemed us from the

00:35:15.839 --> 00:35:17.670
curse of

00:35:17.670 --> 00:35:17.680
the

00:35:17.680 --> 00:35:20.270
law.

00:36:03.480 --> 00:36:06.870
Use your

00:36:06.880 --> 00:36:10.390
authority. Speak to your

00:36:10.400 --> 00:36:13.230
circumstances.

00:36:13.240 --> 00:36:15.630
If you've

00:36:15.640 --> 00:36:17.550
been diagnosed with

00:36:17.560 --> 00:36:19.910
cancer

00:36:19.920 --> 00:36:24.589
or diabetes, tell it to go in the name of Jesus. You have authority in

00:36:24.599 --> 00:36:29.109
all three realms: Heaven, Earth, and Hell.

00:37:17.720 --> 00:37:20.109
We're going to take communion.

00:37:28.319 --> 00:37:30.390
This is

00:37:30.400 --> 00:37:33.109
the meal that heals. Don't just believe

00:37:33.119 --> 00:37:35.910
for

00:37:39.270 --> 00:37:39.280
tomorrow;

00:37:40.839 --> 00:37:43.470
believe

00:37:46.630 --> 00:37:46.640
for

00:37:49.680 --> 00:37:52.550
today.

00:38:24.079 --> 00:38:28.190
Why not now?

00:39:15.560 --> 00:39:18.950
I

00:40:05.230 --> 00:40:05.240
pray

00:40:55.309 --> 00:40:55.319
for

00:41:41.920 --> 00:41:43.589
healing

00:43:22.670 --> 00:43:22.680
for

00:44:48.680 --> 00:44:51.790
diabetes,

00:44:51.800 --> 00:44:54.549
heart disease,

00:45:32.520 --> 00:45:35.150
blood pressure,

00:45:56.150 --> 00:45:56.160
and

00:46:15.119 --> 00:46:17.030
dementia.

00:46:31.720 --> 00:46:33.150
I pray for the children with

00:46:33.160 --> 00:46:35.710
